OL,3,CSouthport inquiry hears of delays in
OL,4,Cattacker's autism diagnosis
OL,6,FAn autism assessment for the Southport
OL,7,Fattacker was delayed by eight months
OL,8,Fdespite a teacher saying she "really
OL,9,Fneeded help" with his diagnosis
OL,10,Ffollowing his disclosures about a
OL,11,Fknife, the public inquiry has heard.
OL,13,FJoanne Hodson, deputy head teacher of
OL,14,Fthe Acorns School emailed the
OL,15,Fcommunity paediatric service in
OL,16,FNovember 2019 explaining an incident
OL,17,Fwhere the teenager - known as AR -
OL,18,Ftold Childline he had been taking a
OL,19,Fknife to the Range High School,
OL,20,FFormby, which led to him being
OL,21,Fexpelled.
