OL,3,CSouthport inquiry hears of delays in
OL,4,Cattacker's autism diagnosis
OL,6,FBut, despite desperately asking the
OL,7,Fteam for help, Lynsey Boggan, clinical
OL,8,Flead of neurodevelopmental services at
OL,9,FAlder Hey Children's NHS Foundation
OL,10,FTrust, said there was a 45-week wait
OL,11,Ffor an appointment.
OL,13,FGiving evidence to the Southport
OL,14,FInquiry, sitting at Liverpool Town
OL,15,FHall, she said the average waiting
OL,16,Ftime for an appointment was 11 weeks.
