OL,3,CSouthport inquiry hears of delays in
OL,4,Cattacker's autism diagnosis
OL,6,FThe inquiry heard Ms Hodson's initial
OL,7,Femail, on 22 November 2019 said: "I
OL,8,Freally need some help with a referral
OL,9,Ffor a young man who is presenting to
OL,10,Fus as ASD."
OL,12,FAfter explaining the knife incident,
OL,13,Fshe added: "I asked him about the
OL,14,Fincident at his admissions meeting and
OL,15,Fhe was monotone, emotionless and very
OL,16,Fmatter of fact about his intentions."
