OL,3,CSouthport inquiry hears of delays in
OL,4,Cattacker's autism diagnosis
OL,6,FShe said they had "serious
OL,7,Fsafeguarding concerns" and AR was
OL,8,Ffixating on another student in his
OL,9,Fclass whom he said was bullying him,
OL,10,Falthough staff had seen no evidence of
OL,11,Fthat.
OL,13,FShe added: "During his ICT lesson AR
OL,14,Fwas searching school shootings in
OL,15,FAmerica. Dad was informed of this but
OL,16,Fthen rang back and said it was untrue."
OL,18,FOn December 3 2019 Ms Hodson emailed
OL,19,Fthe service again to "advise of
OL,20,Ffurther developments and concerns".
