OL,4,Cattacker's autism diagnosis
OL,6,FShe outlined a number of incidents,
OL,7,Fincluding him asking a teacher for a
OL,8,Fpicture of a severed head and speaking
OL,9,Fabout people getting murdered.
OL,11,FMs Boggan, who was not working for
OL,12,FAlder Hey at the time, said she had
OL,13,Fnot been able to find any records of a
OL,14,Fresponse to the school.
OL,16,FNicholas Moss KC, counsel to the
OL,17,Finquiry, said: "Would you agree that
OL,18,Fit's concerning that there is no such
OL,19,Frecord of any response?"
OL,21,FMs Boggan said: "Yes, I would."
OL,26,@yD@POU{D@XO]}D@QOU}D@_O]
