OL,3,CSouthport inquiry hears of delays in
OL,4,Cattacker's autism diagnosis
OL,6,FMinutes from the meeting, shown on
OL,7,Fscreen, recorded his behaviour had
OL,8,Fchanged on transition to high school
OL,9,Fand he had highly fixated interests.
OL,11,FMs Boggan said she took part in a
OL,12,Fvideo call with AR and his father in
OL,13,Fwhich his diagnosis was explained to
OL,14,Fhim.
OL,16,FShe said: "I was aware that there were
OL,17,Fsome incidents where he had harmed
OL,18,Fother people and I think that was why
OL,19,Fwe went around it so sensitively in
OL,20,Fterms of how we delivered the news."
