OL,3,CSouthport inquiry hears of delays in
OL,4,Cattacker's autism diagnosis
OL,6,FThe inquiry heard an assessment by the
OL,7,Fforensic child and adolescent mental
OL,8,Fhealth service (FCAMHS), which works
OL,9,Fwith young people with high-risk
OL,10,Fbehaviour, was not done because they
OL,11,Fwere awaiting the result of the autism
OL,12,Freferral.
OL,14,FBut Ms Boggan said letters from FCAMHS
OL,15,Fwere not put onto the record so the
OL,16,Fautism service was unaware of them.
OL,18,FShe said she would have expected CAMHS
OL,19,Fto re-refer him to the forensic
OL,20,Fservice after his diagnosis.
